dct_description_sm: This collection contains shapefiles representing key statistics from the 2002 Census of the Chile (Censo Nacional de Población, Hogares y Viviendas 2010). The original questionairre and other documentation is included with each download.
System requirements: Geographic Information Systems (GIS) software that reads ESRI shapefile format.
dct_creator_sm: Chile, Dirección de Estadística y Censos
